DATA: directory(30).
*
*SELECTION-SCREEN BEGIN OF BLOCK b1 WITH FRAME.
DATA: p_file TYPE localfile.
*SELECTION-SCREEN END OF BLOCK b1.
*
*INITIALIZATION.
*
*AT SELECTION-SCREEN ON VALUE-REQUEST FOR p_file.
CALL FUNCTION '/SAPDMC/LSM_F4_SERVER_FILE'
  EXPORTING
    directory        = directory
  IMPORTING
    serverfile       = p_file
  EXCEPTIONS
    canceled_by_user = 1
    OTHERS           = 2.
